T* (| Lower or raise the projector screen | Lowering Projector Screen or Retracting Projector) Tj
T* (Screen |) Tj
T* (| Turn the projector or rear TV on or off | Turning Projector / Rear TV On or Turning) Tj
T* (Projector / Rear TV Off |) Tj
T* (| Use microphones | Connecting and Using Microphones |) Tj
T* (| Play sound from a computer | Using Computer Audio |) Tj
T* (| Play sound from a phone, tablet, or laptop over Bluetooth | Bluetooth Pairing |) Tj
T* (| Adjust volume, presets, or muted channels | Using Audio Controls |) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Shutdown Checklist) Tj
T* (1. Turn off the projector or rear TV.) Tj
T* (2. Retract the projector screen if it was lowered.) Tj
T* (3. Mute or lower audio channels on the iPad if needed.) Tj
T* (4. Disconnect personal devices and return cables, microphones, and the iPad to their normal) Tj
T* (locations.) Tj
