T* (This guide explains how to connect devices in Mackey Hall and switch video sources from the) Tj
T* (wall touchscreen.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Connecting Devices) Tj
T* (1. Locate the input ports on the wall outside the Scout Closet, under the projector screen,) Tj
T* (and by the sound system/chair closet wall.) Tj
T* (2. Connect your device to the matching labeled port.) Tj
T* (3. On the touchscreen, select the input that matches the port label you used.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Switching Inputs on the Touchscreen) Tj
T* (1. Go to the wall touchscreen in Mackey Hall.) Tj
T* (2. If you are not on the Homepage or the Video page, press the Home icon in the top-left) Tj
T* (corner.) Tj
T* (3. If you are on the Homepage, press Video to open input controls. If you are already on the) Tj
T* (Video page, continue to the next step.) Tj
T* (Image: Control Screen Homepage) Tj
T* (Press Video on the homepage to open input controls.) Tj
T* (4. On the first Video page, press the input button that matches your connected port.) Tj
T* (5. The selected source will light up blue when it is active.) Tj
T* (Image: Video Controls Page 1) Tj
T* (Select the input that matches your connected port label.) Tj
T* (6. Use the left/right arrows at the bottom to move between Video pages.) Tj
T* (7. On the second Video page, use Freeze to pause the current image or Blank to black out the) Tj
T* (screens.) Tj
T* (Image: Video Controls Page 2) Tj
T* (Use the bottom arrows to switch pages. Freeze and Blank are on the second Video page.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Input Methods) Tj
T* (HDMI Inputs) Tj
T* (Mackey Hall has three HDMI inputs:) Tj
T* (- Church PC HDMI: Located with the VGA and RCA ports under the input selector panel.) Tj
T* (Reserved for the Church PC.) Tj
T* (- HDMI 1: Located near the control touchscreen for personal devices.) Tj
T* (- HDMI 2: Located on the wall outside the Scout Closet, under the projector screen, for) Tj
T* (personal devices.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (HDMI carries both video and audio over one cable.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Church PC HDMI Input) Tj
T* (Image: Church PC HDMI Input) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (HDMI 1 Input) Tj
T* (Image: HDMI 1 Input) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (HDMI 2 Input) Tj
T* (Image: HDMI 2 Input) Tj
T* () Tj
ET
