(VGA Inputs) Tj
T* (There are two VGA input locations in Mackey Hall:) Tj
T* (1. Laptop 1 \(VGA\): Under the input selector panel with its matching 3.5mm audio port.) Tj
T* (2. Laptop 2 \(VGA\): On the wall outside the Scout Closet, under the projector screen, with) Tj
T* (its matching 3.5mm audio port.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (VGA requires two cables for full A/V: VGA \(video\) plus 3.5mm \(audio\).) Tj
