T* (Pulpit Microphone) Tj
T* (1. Locate the pulpit microphone and cable, if not already plugged in.) Tj
T* (2. Plug the microphone into Pulpit 1 or Pulpit 2.) Tj
T* (3. On the wall controls, open Pulpit Wired Mics.) Tj
T* (4. If the selected pulpit channel shows Muted in red, press it once to unmute.) Tj
T* (5. Set level with +1%, -1%, or the slider.) Tj
