T* () Tj
T* (Lapel Microphone \(Wireless\)) Tj
T* (1. Locate the lapel bodypack and lapel mic \(kept in the pulpit when not in use\).) Tj
T* (2. Power: move the top power switch to on.) Tj
T* (3. Clip the lapel mic and begin speaking.) Tj
T* (4. On the wall controls, open Wireless Mics and use channel Lapel.) Tj
T* (5. If channel Lapel shows Muted in red, press it once to unmute.) Tj
T* (6. Set level with +1%, -1%, or the slider.) Tj
