T* (Mute and Level Notes) Tj
T* (- A red Muted button on the wall controls means that channel is muted.) Tj
T* (- Press Muted once to unmute.) Tj
T* (- Use Default to return a channel to its normal level.) Tj
T* (- You can press and hold +1% or -1% for faster continuous changes.) Tj
T* (- Start with lower levels, speak into the microphone, then raise gradually.) Tj
T* (- If a wireless mic has no audio, check battery level and power switch position.) Tj
